hadiths[71]{hadithnumber,text}:
2566,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey musalman aurto! hargiz koi padausan apni dusri padausan ke liye (ma'moolii hadiya ko bhi) haqeer na samjhey, chahe bakri ke khur ka hi kyon na ho.''"
2567,"aap ne Urwa se kaha, mere bhaanjey! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein (ye haal tha ke) ham aik chaand dekhtey, phir doosra dekhtey, phir teesra dekhtey, isi tarah 2-2 mahiney guzar jatey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharon mein (khaanaa pakaaney ke liye) aag na jaltii thi. maine poochha. khala ammaan! phir aap log zinda kis tarah rehti thiin? aap ne farmaya ke sirf 2 kali chizon khajoor aur pani par. albatta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand Ansari padosi they. jinke paas doodh dene wali bakriyan thin aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan bhi unka doodh tohfe ke taur par pahuncha jaya kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey hamein bhi pilaa diya kartey they."
2568,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar mujhey bazu aur paaey (ke gosht ( par bhi dawat di jaey to main qabool kar loonga aur mujhey bazu ya paaey (ke gosht) ka tohfa bheja jaey to usey bhi qabool kar loonga.''
2569,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik muhaajira aurat ke paas ( apna aadmi ( bhejaa. unka aik ghulam badhii tha. unse Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ghulam se hamarey liye lakdiyon ka aik member banaaney ke liye kahin . chunanche unhon-ne apne ghulam se kaha, wo Ghaaba se ja kar jhaau kaat laya aur usi ka aik member bana diya. jab wo member bana chukey to us aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein kelha bheja ke member bin kar taiyaar hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahlwaayaa ke usey mere paas bhijwa dein. jab log usey laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud usey uthaya aur jahan tum ab dekh rahe ho. wahin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey rakha."
2570,"Makka ke rastey mein aik jagah main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sathiyon ke sath betha hua tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se aagey qiyam farma they. (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) aur log to ehram baandhey huey they lekin mera ehram nahi tha. mere sathiyon ne aik gorkhar dekha. main us waqt apni jootii gaanthney mein mashghool tha. un logon ne mujh ko kuchh khabar nahi di. lekin unki khahish yahi thi ke kisi tarah mein gorkhar ko dekh loon. chunanche maine jo nazar uthai to gorkhar dikhai diya. main fauran ghodey ke paas gaya aur is par zeen kas kar Sawar ho gaya, magar ittifaq se ( jaldi mein) kodaa aur neza donon bhool gaya. isliye maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke wo mujhey kodaa aur neza utha dein. unhon-ne kaha hargiz nahi qism Allah ki, ham tumharey (shikaar mein) kisi qism ki madad nahi kar saktey. (kyonke ham sab log haalate-ehraam mein hain) mujhey is par ghussa aaya aur maine khud hi utar kar donon cheezein ley liin. phir Sawar ho kar gorkhar par hamla kya aur usko shikar kar laya. wo mar bhi chuka tha. ab logon ne kaha ke usey khana chahiye lekin phir ehram ki haalat mein usey khaney (ke jawaaz) par shuba hua. (lekin kuchh logon ne shuba nahi kya aur gosht khaya ( phir ham aagey badhey aur maine us gorkhar ka aik bazu chipa rakha tha. jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunchey to uske mutaalliq aap se sawal kya, (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram ki haalat mein rahnewaalon ke liye shikar ke gosht khaney ka fatwa diyaa) aur malum farmaya ke usmein se kuchh bacha hua gosht tumharey paas maujood bhi hai? maine kaha ke ji haan ! aur wahi bazu Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khaya, yahan tak ke wo khatm ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi us waqt ehram se they ( abu-Hazim ne kaha ke) mujh se yahi hadis Zaid-bin-Aslam ne bayan ki, unse Ata-bin-Yasar ne aur unse abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
2571,"(eik martaba) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey usi ghar mein tashrif laey aur pani talab farmaya, hamarey paas aik bakri thi, usey ham ne dohaa. phir maine usi kuwein ka pani mila kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (lassii bana kar) pesh kya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf baithey huey they aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) samney they aur aik dehati Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daain taraf tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pi kar farigh huey to (piyaaley mein kuchh doodh bach gaya tha us liye) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey dehati ko ata farmaya, (kyonke wo daain taraf tha) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, daain taraf baithney waale, daain taraf baithney waley hi haq rakhtey hain. to khabardaar daain taraf hi se shuru kiya karo. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke yahi sunnat hai, yahi sunnat hai, teen martaba (aap ne is baat ko dohraayaa)."
2572,"marruz-zohraan naam ke jagah mein ham ne aik khargosh ka peechhaa kya. log (uske peechhey) daudey aur usey thakaa diya aur maine qareeb pahunch kar usey pakad liya. phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan laya. unhon-ne usey zabah kya aur uske peechhey ka ya donon raanon ka gosht Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. (Shoba ne baad mein yaqin ke saath) kaha ke donon raanein unhon-ne bheji thin, usmein koi shak nahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey qabool farmaya tha maine puchha aur is mein se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh tanaawul bhi farmaayaa? unhon-ne bayan kya ke haan! kuchh khaya tha. iske baad phir unhon-ne kaha ke aap ne wo hadiya qabool farma liya tha."
2573,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gorkhar ka tohfa pesh kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt maqaame-Abwaa ya maqaame-Wadaan mein they (raawii ko shuba hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka tohfa wapas kar diya. phir unke chehrey par (ranj ke aasaar) dekh kar farmaya ke maine ye tohfa sirf isliye wapas kya hai ke ham ehram baandhey huey hain.
2574,"log ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein) tohfey bhejney ke liye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka intizar kya kartey they. apne hadiyon se, ya us khas din ke intizar se ( rawi ko shak hai) log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khushi hasil karna chahtey they."
2575,"unki khala umme-Hufaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein paneer , ghi aur goh ( saahina (ke tohfey bhejey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paneer aur ghi mein se to khaya lekin goh pasand na honey ki wjah se chhod di. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (usi ( dastar-khuwaan par goh ( saahina ( ko bhi khaya gaya aur agar wo haram hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke dastar-khuwaan par kyon khaaii jati."
2576,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab koi khaney ki cheez laai jati to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) malum farmatey ye tohfa hai ya sadqa ? agar kaha jata ke sadqe hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ashaab se farmatey ke khaao , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud na khaatey aur agar kaha jata ke tohfa hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud bhi hath badhaatey aur sahaba ke sath usey khaatey ."
2577,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik martaba gosht pesh kya gaya aur ye bataya gaya ke ye Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko kisi ne bataur sadqe ke diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''unke liye ye sadqa hai aur hamarey liye (jab unke yahan se pahuncha to) hadiya hai.''
2578,"maine ye hadis Abdur-Rehman se suni thi aur unhon-ne Qasim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke unhon-ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko) aazad karne ke liye) khareednaa chaha. lekin unke maalikon ne 'walaa' ki shart apne liye lagaaii. jab iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa: to unhein khareed kar aazad kar de, 'walaa' to usi ke sath qaaim hoti hai jo aazad kare. aur Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ( sadqa ka ( gosht aaya tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha ye wahi hai jo Barira ko sadqe mein mila hai. ye unke liye to sadqa hai lekin hamarey liye ( chunkey unke ghar se bataur hadiya mila hai) hadiya hai aur) aazadi ke baad Barira ko) ikhtiyar diya gaya tha (ke agar chaahein to apne nikah ko fasakh kar sakti hain) Abdur-Rehman ne puchha Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke khawind (Mughees (Raziallahu anhu)) ghulam they ya aazad ? Shoba ne bayan kya ke maine Abdur-Rehman se unke khawind ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi wo ghulam they ya aazaad."
2579,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif le gaey aur malum farmaya, kya koi cheez ( khaney ki) tumharey paas hai? unhon-ne kaha ke umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan jo aap ne sadqa ki bakri bheji thi, uska gosht unhon-ne bheja hai. iske siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo apni jagah pahunch chukii."
2580,log tohfey bhejney ke liye meri baari ka intizar kya kartey they. aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha meri saukanein (nabi ki beeviyan rz) jama thin us waqt unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( bataur shikayat logon ki us ravish ka ( zikr kya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein koi jawab nahi diya.
2581,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon 2 giroh mein thin. aik main Aaisha, Hafsa , Safiya aur Sauda (Raziallahu anha) aur dusri mein Umme-Salma aur Baqiiya tamam paak beeviyan (Raziallahu anhu) thin. musalmanon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke sath mohabbat ka ilm tha isliye jab kisi ke paas koi tohfa hota aur wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh karna chahta to intizar karta. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar ki baari hoti to tohfa dene waley sahib apna tohfa Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejtey. is par Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki jamat ki paak beeviyon ne aapas mein mashwara kya aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat karein taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon se farma dein ke jisey aap ke yahan tohfa bhejna ho wo jahan bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hon wahin bheja kare. chunanche un beeviyon ke mashwara ke mutabiq unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein koi jawab nahi diya. phir un khawaateen ne puchha to unhon-ne bata diya ke mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya. paak beeviyon ne kaha ke phir aik martaba kaho. unhon-ne bayan kya, phir jab aap ki baari aai to dobara unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya. us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey iska koi jawab hi nahi diya. beeviyon ne us martaba unse kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us mas'ale par bulwao to sahii. jab unki baari aai to unhon-ne phir kaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba farmaya, Aaisha ke barey mein mujhey takleef na do. Aaisha ke siwa apni beeviyon mein se kisi ke kapdey mein bhi mujh par wahi nazil nahi hoti hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad par unhon-ne arz kya, aapko takleef pahunchaney ki wjah se main Allah ke huzoor mein tauba karti hun. phir un paak beeviyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko bulaya aur unke zariey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ye kahlwaayaa ke aap ki beeviyan Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ke barey mein Allah ke liye aap se insaf chahti hain. chunanche unhon-ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat cheet ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, meri beti ! kya tum wo pasand nahi karti jo main pasand karun? unhon-ne jawab diya ke kyon nahi. iske baad wo wapas aa gain aur beeviyon ko itlaa di. unhon-ne unse phir dobara khidmat nabwi mein janey ke liye kaha, lekin aap ne dobara janey se inkar kya to unhon-ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko bhejaa. wo khidmat nabwi mein hazir huin to unhon-ne sakht guftgu ki aur kaha ke aap ki beeviyan abu-Qahaafa ki beti ke barey mein aap se Allah ke liye insaf maangtii hain aur unki awaz unchi ho gaee. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) wahin baithi hui thin. unhon-ne (unke munh par) unhein bhi bura bhala kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf dekhney lagey ke wo kuchh boltii hain ya nahi. rawi ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi bol padiin aur Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ki baton ka jawab dene lagiin aur aakhir unhein khamosh kar diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf dekh kar farmaya ke ye Abu-Bakar ki beti hai. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke aakhir kalam Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke waqia se mutaalliq Hisham-bin-Urwa ne aik aur shakhs se bayan kya hai. unhon-ne Zohri se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman se aur Abu-Marwaan ne bayan kya ke Hisham se aur unhon-ne Urwa se ke log tohfey bhejney ke liye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka intizar kya kartey they aur Hisham ki aik riwayat Quraish ke aik sahib aur aik doosrey sahib se jo ghulaamon mein se they, bhi hai. wo Zohri se naql kartey hain aur wo Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham se ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne (andar aaney ki) ijazat chahi to main us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ki khidmat mein maujood thi."
2582,"mujh se Samama bin-Abdullah ne bayan kya, azra ne kaha ke main Samama bin-Abdullah ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne mujhey khushbu inayat farmai aur bayan kya ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) khushbu ko wapas nahi kartey they. Samama ne kaha ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka guman tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khushbu ko wapas nahi farmaya kartey they."
2583,"jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab farmaya aur Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq sana ke baad aap ne farmaya : ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai tauba karke hamarey paas aaey hain aur main yahi behtar samajhta hun ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se ( qaidiyon ko) wapas karna chahey wo wapas kar de aur jo ye chahey ke unhein unka hissey miley (to wo bhi wapas kar de) aur hamein Allah Taala (iske baad) sabse pehli jo ghaneemat dega, usmein se ham usey muaawaza de dengey. logon ne kaha ham apni khushi se (unke qaidi wapas karke (aap ka irshad taslim kartey hain."
2584,"jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab farmaya aur Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq sana ke baad aap ne farmaya : ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai tauba karke hamarey paas aaey hain aur main yahi behtar samajhta hun ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se ( qaidiyon ko) wapas karna chahey wo wapas kar de aur jo ye chahey ke unhein unka hissey miley (to wo bhi wapas kar de) aur hamein Allah Taala (iske baad) sabse pehli jo ghaneemat dega, usmein se ham usey muaawaza de dengey. logon ne kaha ham apni khushi se (unke qaidi wapas karke (aap ka irshad taslim kartey hain."
2585,"ham se Musaddad ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Esa-bin-Yonus ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Hisham ne, unse unke walid ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hadiyaa qabool farma liya kartey they, lekin uska badla bhi de diya kartey they; us hadis ko Wakee or Muhaazir ne bhi riwayat kiya hai, magar unhoney isko Hisham se, unhoney apne bap se unhoney Hazrat Aaisha se ke alfaz nahi kahey."
2586,"unke walid unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laey aur arz kya ke maine apne us betey ko aik ghulam bataur hiba diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kya aisa hi ghulam apne doosrey ladkon ko bhi diya hai? unhon-ne kaha nahi, to aap ne farmaya ke phir ( unse bhi) wapas ley ley."
2587,"wo member par bayan kar rahe they ke mere bap ne mujhey aik Atiya diya, to Umra-binte-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) (Naumaan ki waalida) ne kaha ke jab tak aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is par gawah na banaaein main razi nahi ho saktii. chunanche (haazire-khidmat ho kar) unhon-ne arz kya ke Umra-binteRawaaha se apne betey ko maine aik Atiya diya to unhon-ne kaha ke pahley main aapko is par gawah bana loon, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke usi jaisa Atiya tum ne apni tamam aulad ko diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se daro aur apni aulad ke darmyan insaf ko qaaim rakho. chunanche wo wapas huey aur hadiya wapas ley liya."
2588,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari badhii aur takleef shadeed ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon se mere ghar mein bimari ke din guzarney ki ijazat chahi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko beeviyon ne ijazat de di to aap is tarah tashrif laey ke donon qadam zameen par ragad kha rahe they. aap us waqt Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik aur sahib ke darmyan they. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke phir maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki us hadis ka zikr Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kya. to unhon-ne mujh se poochha, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jinka naam nahi liya, jantey ho wo kon they? maine kaha ke nahi? aap ne farmaya ke wo Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) they."
2589,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' apna hiba wapas leney wala us kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karke phir chaat jata hai.''
2590,"maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mere paas sirf wahi maal hai jo ( mere shauhar ( Zuber ne mere paas rakha hua hai, to kya main usmein se sadqa kar sakti hon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' sadqa karo, jod ke na rakho, kahin tum se bhii. ( Allah ki taraf se na ( rok liya jaaey.''"
2591,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kharch kya kar, gunah na kar, taake tumhen bhi gin ke na miley aur jod ke na rakho, taake tum se bhi Allah Taala (apni ne'maton ko) na chipa ley.'"
2592,"unhon-ne aik londi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat liye baghair aazad kar di. phir jis din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baari aap ke ghar aaney ki thi, unhon-ne khidmat nabwi mein arz kya, ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aapko malum bhi hua, maine aik londi aazad kar di hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha tum ne aazad kar diya? unhon-ne arz kya ke haan! farmaya ke agar iske bajaey tum ne apne nanihaal walon ko di hoti to tumhen us se bhi zyada sawab miltaa. us hadis ko Bukair-bin-Muzir ne Amr-bin-Haris se, unhon-ne Bukair se, unhon-ne Kureb se riwayat kya ke Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne apni londi aazad kar di. akheer tak."
2593,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar ka irada kartey to apni beeviyon ke liye Qura andazi kartey aur jinka Qura nikal aata unhiin ko apne sath ley jatey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye bhi tariqa tha ke apni tamam beeviyon ke liye eik-eik din aur raat ki baari muqarrar kar di thi, albatta ( aakhir mein) Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni baari Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko de di thi, us se unka maqsad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raza hasil karni thi."
2594,(bayaan kya ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne apni aik londi aazad ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ''agar wo tumharey nanihaal walon ko di jati to tumhen zyada sawab miltaa.''
2595,"maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! meri 2 padosi hain, to mujhey kis ke ghar hadiya bhejna chahiye ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jiska darwaza tum se qareeb ho.''"
2596,"unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik gorkhar hadiya kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt maqam Abwaa ya maqam Wadaan mein they aur ehram ki haalat mein they. aap ne wo gorkhar wapas kar diya. Sa'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke iske baad jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere chehrey par) narazagi ka asar ( hadiya ki waapsii ki wjah se dekha, to farmaya '' hadiya wapas karna munasib to na tha lekin baat ye hai ke ham ehram baandhey huey hain.''"
2597,"qabila Azd ke aik sahabi ko jinhein ibne- Utbia kehtey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sadqa wsool karne ke liye aamil banaya. phir jab wo wapas aaey to kaha ke ye tum logon ka hai (yani baitul-maal ka (aur ye mujhey hadiya mein mila hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo apne walid ya apni walida ke ghar mein kyon na betha raha. dekhta wahan bhi unhein hadiya milta hai ya nahi. us zaat ki qism ! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. us (maal zakaat) mein se agar koi shakhs kuchh bhi) naajaaiz ( le-lega to qiyamat ke din usey wo apni gardan par uthaey huey aayega. agar oont hai to wo apni awaz nikaaltaa hua aayega, gaaey hai to wo apni aur agar bakri hai to wo apni awaz nikaaltii hogi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath uthaey yahan tak ke ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baghl ki safedi bhi dekh li (aur farmaya) aey Allah ! kya maine tera hukm pahuncha diya. aey Allah ! kya maine tera hukm pahuncha diya. teen martaba (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ( ."
2598,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se wada farmaya, agar Bahrain ka maal (jiziye ka ( aaya to main tumhen itnaa-itnaa teen lap maal doonga. lekin Bahrain se maal aaney se pahley hi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat farma gaey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik manaadii se ye elaan karne ke liye kaha ke jis se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka koi wada ho ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par iska koi qarz ho to wo hamarey paas aaey. chunanche main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan gaya aur kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se wada kya tha. to unhon-ne teen lap bhar kar mujhey diye."
2599,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand qubaaein taqseem kiin aur Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ko usmein se aik bhi nahi di. unhon-ne (mujh se) kaha, betey chalo, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein chalein. main unke sath chalaa. phir unhon-ne kaha ke andar jao aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz karo ke main aap ka muntazir khada hua hon, chunanche main andar gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bula laya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt unhein qubaaon mein se aik Quba pahney huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine ye tumharey liye chipa rakhi thi, lo ab ye tumhari hai. Miswar ne bayan kya ke (mere waalid) Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ne Quba ki taraf dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Makhrima ! khush ho ya nahin?''"
2600,"aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga ke main to halaak ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''kya baat huii? '' arz kya ke Ramazan mein maine apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya '' tumharey paas koi ghulam hai? ''kaha ke nahi. phir malum farmaya ''kya 2 mahiney pai-dar-pai rozey rakh saktey ho? ''kaha ke nahi. phir malum farmaya ''kya sath miskinon ko khana de saktey ho? '' is par bhi jawab tha ke nahi. bayan kya ke itney mein aik Ansari arq laey. ( arq khajoor ke patton ka bana hua aik tokraa hota tha jis mein khajoor rakhi jati thi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya '' usey ley ja aur sadqa kar de'' unhon-ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah! kya apne se zyada zarurat mand par sadqa kar dun? aur us zaat ki qasam! jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai ke sarey Madiney mein ham se zyada mohtaaj aur koi gharaana nahi hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir jaa, apne hi ghar walon ko khilaa de.''"
2601,"Uhud ki ladai mein unke bap Shahid ho gaey (aur qarz chhod gaey) qarz-khaahon ne taqazey mein badi shiddat ki, to main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is silsiley mein guftgu ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke wo mere baagh ki khajoor ley lein (jo bhi hon) aur mere walid ko (jo baqi reh jaey wo qarz) maaf kar dein. lekin unhon-ne inkar kya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera baagh unhein nahi diya aur na unke liye phal tudwaaey. balke farmaya ke kal subah main tumharey yahan aaunga . subah ke waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur khajoor ke darakhton mein tahaltey rahe aur barkat ki dua farmatey rahe phir maine phal tod kar qarz-khaahon ke sarey qarz ada kar diye aur mere paas khajoor bach bhi gaee. iske baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko waaqie ki itlaa di. umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi wahin baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, Umar! sun rahe ho? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, hamein to pahley se malum hai ke aap Allah ke sachey rasool hain. qism Allah ki! ismein kisi shak w shubeh ki gunjaaish hi nahi ke aap Allah ke sachey rasool hain."
2602,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein peeney ko kuchh laayaa, (doodh ya paanii) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nosh farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daain taraf aik bachcha betha tha aur badey boodhey log baain taraf baithey huey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bachchey se farmaya ke agar to ijazat de (to bacha hua paanii) main un badey logon ko de dun? lekin us ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! aap ke joothe mein se milney waley kisi hisse ka main eisaar nahi kar sakta. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyala jhatkey ke sath usi ki taraf badha diya."
2603,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (safar se lot kar) masjid mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( mere oont ki qeemat ( ada ki aur kuchh zyada bhi diya.
2604,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko safar mein aik oont bechaa tha. jab ham Madina pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke masjid mein ja kar do rakaat Namaz padh, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wazan kya. Shoba ne bayan kya, mera khayal hai ke (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) mere liye wazan kya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne) aur (is paldey ko jis mein sikka tha) jhukaa diya. (taake mujhey zyada miley) usmein se kuchh thoda sa mere paas jab se mehfooz tha. lekin Sham (Syria) waley (umwii lashakr) yaume-harra ke mauqe par mujh se chheen kar ley gaey."
2605,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein kuchh peeney ko laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daain taraf aik bachcha tha aur qaum ke badey log baain taraf they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey se farmaya ke kya tumhari taraf se uski ijazat hai ke main bacha hua pani un buzurgon ko de dun? to us bachchey ne kaha ke nahi qism Allah ki! main aap se milney waley apne hisse ka hargiz eisaar nahi kar sakta. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashroob unki taraf jhatkey ke sath badha diya.
2606,"aik shakhs ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par qarz tha (us ne sakhti ke sath taqaza kya) to sahaba uski taraf badhey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usey chhod do, haq waley ko kuchh na kuchh kehney ki gunjaaish hoti hi hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uske liye aik oont usi ke oont ki Umr ka khareed kar usey de do. sahaba ne arz kya ke us se achi Umr ka hi oont mil raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usi ko khareed kar de do ke tum mein sabse achchha aadmi wo hai jo qarz ke ada karne mein sabse achchha ho."
2607,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke unke amwaal aur qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jayen to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya mere sath jitni badi jamat hai usey bhi tum dekh rahe ho aur sabse zyada sachchii baat hi mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai isliye tum log in 2 chizon mein se aik hi ley saktey ho, ya apne qaidi ley lo ya apna maal . maine tumhara pahley hi intizar kya tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Taaif se waapsii par taqriban das din tak ( maqam Jaarana mein) un logon ka intizar farmatey rahe. phir jab un logon ke samney ye baat poori tarah waazeh ho gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki sirf aik hi cheez wapas farma saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham apne qaidiyon hi ko (waapas lenaa) pasand kartey hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar musalmanon ko khitab kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki uski shaan ke mutabiq tareef bayan ki aur farmaya, ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai hamarey paas ab tauba karke aaey hain. mera khayal ye hai ke unhein unke qaidi wapas kar dun. isliye jo sahib apni khushi se wapas karna chaahein wo aisa kar lein aur jo log ye chahtey hon ke apne hissey ko na chhodein balke ham unhein iske badley mein sabse pehli ghaneemat ke maal mein se muaawaza dein, to wo bhi (apne maujooda qaidiyon ko) wapas kar dein. sab sahaba ne is par kaha, ya Rasulullah ! ham apni khushi se unhein wapas kartey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin waazeh taur par us waqt ye malum na ho saka ke kon apni khushi se dene ke liye taiyaar hai aur kon nahi. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas jayen aur tumharey zimmedaar log tumhara mamla la kar pesh karein. chunanche sab log wapas ho gaey aur numaaindon ne unse guftgu ki aur wapas ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya ke tamam logon ne khushi se ijazat de di hai. qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq hamein yahi baat malum hui hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ye Zohri (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ka aakhiri qaul tha. yani ye ke qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq hamein yahi baat malum hui hai."
2608,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke unke amwaal aur qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jayen to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya mere sath jitni badi jamat hai usey bhi tum dekh rahe ho aur sabse zyada sachchii baat hi mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai isliye tum log in 2 chizon mein se aik hi ley saktey ho, ya apne qaidi ley lo ya apna maal . maine tumhara pahley hi intizar kya tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Taaif se waapsii par taqriban das din tak ( maqam Jaarana mein) un logon ka intizar farmatey rahe. phir jab un logon ke samney ye baat poori tarah waazeh ho gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki sirf aik hi cheez wapas farma saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham apne qaidiyon hi ko (waapas lenaa) pasand kartey hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar musalmanon ko khitab kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki uski shaan ke mutabiq tareef bayan ki aur farmaya, ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai hamarey paas ab tauba karke aaey hain. mera khayal ye hai ke unhein unke qaidi wapas kar dun. isliye jo sahib apni khushi se wapas karna chaahein wo aisa kar lein aur jo log ye chahtey hon ke apne hissey ko na chhodein balke ham unhein iske badley mein sabse pehli ghaneemat ke maal mein se muaawaza dein, to wo bhi (apne maujooda qaidiyon ko) wapas kar dein. sab sahaba ne is par kaha, ya Rasulullah ! ham apni khushi se unhein wapas kartey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin waazeh taur par us waqt ye malum na ho saka ke kon apni khushi se dene ke liye taiyaar hai aur kon nahi. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas jayen aur tumharey zimmedaar log tumhara mamla la kar pesh karein. chunanche sab log wapas ho gaey aur numaaindon ne unse guftgu ki aur wapas ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya ke tamam logon ne khushi se ijazat de di hai. qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq hamein yahi baat malum hui hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ye Zohri (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ka aakhiri qaul tha. yani ye ke qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq hamein yahi baat malum hui hai."
2609,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik oont bataur qarz liya, qarz-khaah taqaza karne aaya (aur naazebaa guftgu ki) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' haq waley ko kehney ka haq hota hai.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se achi Umr ka oont usey dila diya aur farmaya ''tum mein afzal wo hai jo ada karne mein sabse behtar ho.''"
2610,"wo safar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik sarkash oont par Sawar they. wo oont Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi aagey badh jaya karta tha. isliye unke walid ( umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ko tanbeeh karni padtii thi ke aey Abdullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aagey kisi ko na hona chahiye phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ! ke umr ! usey mujhey bech de. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ye to aap hi ka hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khareed liya. phir farmaya, Abdullah ye ab tera hai. jis tarah to chahey istemal kar."
2611,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they aur main aik sarkash oont par Sawar tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ye oont mujhey bech de chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khareed liya aur phir farmaya Abdullaah! to ye oont ley ja ( maine ye tujh ko bakhsh diyaa) .
2612,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke masjid ke darwazey par aik reshamii hulla (bik raha) hai. aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya, ke kya achchha hota agar aap usey khareed letey aur Juma ke din aur wufood ki mulaqat ke mauqe par usey pahan liya kartey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska jawab ye diya ke isey wahi log pahntey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi hoga. kuchh dinon baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan bahut se ( reshamii ( hulley aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hulla unmein se umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi inayat farmaya, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par arz kya ke aap ye mujhey pahnney ke liye inayat farma rahe hain. halanke aap khud utaarid ke hullon ke barey mein jo kuchh farmana tha farma chukey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine usey tumhen pahnney ke liye nahi diya hai. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apne aik mushrik bhai ko de diya, jo makke mein rehta tha."
2613,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif le gaey, lekin andar nahi gaey. iske baad Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ghar aaey to Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne zikr kya (ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein tashrif nahi laey ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska zikr jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine uske darwazey par dhaarii daar parda latkaa dekha tha (is liye wapas chala aayaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey duniya (ki aaraaish w zebaaish) se kya sarokaar. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne aa kar unse Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki guftgu ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke aap mujhey jis tarah ka chaahein is silsiley mein hukm farmaein . (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab ye baat pahunchi to) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke falan ghar mein usey bhijwa dein. unhein uski zarurat hai."
2614,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik reshamii hulla hadiye mein diya to maine usey pahan liya. lekin jab ghussey ke aasaar chehre par dekhey to usey apni aurton mein phaad kar taqseem kar diya.
2615,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein dabeez qism ke resham ka aik jubba hadiye ke taur par pesh kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske istemal se (mardon ko) mana farmatey they. sahaba ko badi hairat hui (ke kitna umda resham hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (tumhein is par hairat hai) us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai, jannat mein Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke roomaal us se bhi zyada khoobsurat hain."
2616,dauma (Tabook ke qareeb aik maqaam) ke Akeedar ( nasrani ( ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hadiya bheja tha.
2617,"aik Yahudi aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein zahar mila hua bakri ka gosht laaii, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se kuchh khaya (lekin fauran hi farmaya ke usmein zahar padaa hua hai) phir jab usey laya gaya (aur usne zahar dalney ka iqrar bhi kar liyaa) to kaha gaya ke kyon na usey qatl kar diya jaey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. us zahar ka asar maine hamesha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke taaloo mein mehsus kya."
2618,"ham aik so tees (130) aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eik safar mein) they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya kisi ke sath khaney ki bhi koi cheez hai? aik sahabi ke sath taqriban aik saa khana ( aata ( tha. wo aata goondhaa gaya. phir aik lambaa-tadangaa mushrik pareshan haal bakriyan haanktaa hua aaya. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ye bechney ke liye hain. ya kisi ka Atiya hai ya aap ne (atiya ki bajaey) hiba farmaya, usne kaha ke nahi bechney ke liye hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se aik bakri kharidi phir wo zabah ki gaee. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski kalejii bhoonney ke liye kaha, qism Allah ki aik so tees ashaab mein se har aik ko us kalejii mein se kaat ke diya. jo maujood they unhein to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fauran hi de diya aur jo us waqt maujood nahi they unka hissey mehfooz rakh liya. phir bakri ke gosht ko 2 badi piyaalon mein rakha gaya aur sab ne khub sair ho kar khaayaa. jo kuchh piyaalon mein bach gaya tha usey oont par rakh kar ham wapas laey. ya isi tarah kuch kaha."
2619,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke aik shakhs ke yahan aik reshamii joda bik raha hai. to aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke aap ye joda khareed lijiye taake Juma ke din aur jab koi wafad aaey to aap usey pehna karein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey to wo log pahntey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi hota. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bahut se reshamii jodey aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik joda umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhejaa. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main isey kis tarah pahan sakta hun jabke aap khud hi iske mutaalliq jo kuchh irshad farmana tha, farma chukey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhen pahnney ke liye nahi diya balke isliye diya ke tum isey bech do ya kisi (ghair muslim) ko pehna do. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Makke main apne aik bhai ke ghar bhej diya jo abhi Islam nahi laya tha."
2620,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein meri walida (Qutaila- binte- abdul-Uzzaa) jo mushrika thin, mere yahan aaiin. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, maine ye bhi kaha ke wo (mujh se mulaqat ki) bahut khaahishmand hain, to kya main apni walida ke sath sila rehmii kar sakti hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, apni walida ke sath sila rehmii kar."
2621,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''apnaa diya hua hadiya wapas leney wala aisa hai jaisey apni ki hui qai ko chaatney waalaa.''
2622,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ham musalmanon ko buri misal na ikhtiyar karni chahiye us shakhs ki si jo apna diya hua hadiya wapas ley ley, wo us kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai khud chaatta hai.''"
2623,"unhon-ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. aap ne farmaya ke maine aik ghoda Allah ke rastey mein jihad ke liye (eik shakhs ko) diyaa). jisey maine wo ghoda diya tha, us ne usey dublaa kar diya. isliye mera irada hua ke us se apna wo ghoda khareed loon, mera ye bhi khayal tha ke wo shakhs wo ghoda sastey daamon par bech dega. lekin jab maine iske barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to aap ne farmaya ke tum usey na khareedo, chahe tumhen wo aik hi dirham mein kyon na de. kyonke apne sadqe ko wapas leney wala shakhs us kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni hi qai khud chaatta hai."
2624,2 makan aur aik hujra Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ko inayat farmaya tha (jo wiraasat mein unhein milnaa chahiye ( khaleefa Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne puchha ke tumharey haq mein us da'wey par gawah kon hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) . Marwan ne aapko bulaya to aap ne gawahi di ke waqei Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ko 2 makan aur aik hujra diya tha. Marwan ne aap ki gawahi par faisla unke haq mein kar diya.
2625,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umra ke mutaalliq faisla kya tha ke wo uska ho jata hai jisey hiba kya gaya ho.
2626,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''umraa jaaiz hai.'' aur Ata ne kaha ke mujh se Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah bayan kya.
2627,"Madiney par (dushman ke hamley ka ( khof tha. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se aik ghoda jiska naam mandoob tha mus'taar liya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par Sawar huey (sahaaba bhi sath they) phir jab wapas huey to farmaya, hamein to koi khatre ki cheez nazar na aaii, albatta ye ghoda samandar ki tarah (tez daudtaa) paya."
2628,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap Qitr ( Yaman ka aik dabeez khurdaraa kapda ( ki qamees qeemtii panch dirham ki pahney huey thin. aap ne (mujh se) farmaya, zara nazar utha kar meri us londi ko to dekh. usey ghar mein bhi ye kapdey pahnney se inkar hai. halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein mere paas usi ki aik qamees thi. jab koi ladki dulhan banai jati to mere yahan aadmi bhej kar wo qamees aariyatan mangaa leti thi."
2629,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya hi umda hai hadiya us doodh dene wali ontni ka jisne abhi haal hi mein bachcha janaa ho aur doodh dene wali bakri ka jo subah w Sham apne doodh se bartan bhar deti hai. ham se Abdullaah-bin-Yoosuf aur Ismail ne bayan kya, unse Imam Malik ne bayan kya ke (doodh dene wali ontni ka ( sadqa kya hi umda hai."
2630,"jab muhajireen Makka se Madina aaey to unke sath koi bhi saman na tha. Ansar zameen aur jaaidaad waley they. Ansar ne muhajireen se ye mamla kar liya ke wo apne baghaat mein se unhein har saal phal diya karengey aur uske badley muhajireen unke baghaat mein kaam kya karein. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida Umme-Sulaim jo Abdullaah-bin-abii-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ki bhi walida thin, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khajoor ka aik baagh hadiya de diya tha lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo baagh apni londi umme-Aiman (Raziallahu anhu) jo Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida thin, inayat farma diya. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke mujhey Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khaibar ke yahudiyon ki jang se farigh huey aur Madina tashrif laey to muhajireen ne Ansar ko unke tohfey wapas kar diye jo unhon-ne phalon ki sura mein de rakhey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida ka baagh bhi wapas kar diya aur umme-Aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ko iske bajaey apne baagh mein se (kuchh darakht) inayat farma diye. Ahmed bin shabeeb ne bayan kya, unhein unke walid ne khabar di aur unhein Yunus ne isi tarah albatta apni riwayat mein bajaaey (مكانهن من حائطه) ke (مكانهن من خالصه‏) bayaan kya."
2631,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, chalis (40) khaslatein jin mein sabse aalaa w buland. doodh dene wali bakri ka hadiya karna hai. aisi hain ke jo shakhs unmein se aik khaslat par bhi aamil hoga sawab ki niyat se aur Allah ke waadey ko sachcha samajhtey huey to Allah Taala uski wjah se usey jannat mein dakhil karega. Hassan ne kaha ke doodh dene wali bakri ke hadiye ko chhod kar ham ne salam ka jawab denaa, chheenkney waley ka jawab dena aur takleef dene wali cheez ko rastey se hata dene wghaira ka shumaar kya, to sab pandarah khaslatein bhi ham shumaar na kar sakey."
2632,"ham mein se bahut se ashaab ke paas faaltu zameen bhi thi, unhon-ne kaha tha ke tehai ya chothai ya nisf ki batai par ham kyon na usey de diya karein. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jiske paas zameen ho to usey khud bonii chahiye ya phir kisi apne bhai ko hadiya kar deni chahiye aur agar aisa nahi karta to phir zameen apne paas rakhey rahe.''"
2633,aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hijrat ke liye poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya'' Allah tum par raham kare. hijrat ka to bada hi dushwar mamla hai. tumharey paas oont bhi hai?'' unhon-ne kaha ji haan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya'' aur iska sadqa (zakaat) bhi ada kartey ho?'' unhon-ne kaha ji haan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''usmein se kuchh hadiya bhi detey ho? ''unhon-ne kaha ji haan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya'' to tum usey pani pilaaney ke liye ghaat par ley janey waley din dohtey hogey?'' unhon-ne kaha ji haan! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''samandaron ke paar bhi agar tum amal karogey to Allah Taala tumharey amal mein se koi cheez kam nahi karega.''
2634,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba aisey khet ki taraf tashrif le gaey jiski kheti lahlaha rahi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''ye kis ka hai?'' sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke falan ne usey kiraaye par liya hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar wo hadiyatan de deta to us se behtar tha ke is par aik muqarrara ujrat wsool kartaa.''"
2635,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ne Saara (Alaihissalam) ke sath hijrat ki to unhein badshah ne Aajar ko (yani Hajra (Alaihissalam) ko) Atiya mein de diya. phir wo wapas huin aur Ibrahim se kaha, dekha aap ne Allah Taala ne kaafir ko kis tarah zaleel kya aur aik ladki khidmat ke liye bhi de di. Ibne-Sirin ne kaha, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke badshah ne Hajra ko unki khidmat ke liye de diya tha."
2636,"maine apne bap se suna wo bayan kartey they ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine aik ghoda Allah ke rastey mein jihad ke liye aik shakhs ko de diya tha, phir maine dekha ke wo usey bech raha hai. isliye maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke usey waapasi mein hi khareed loon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''is ghodey ko na khareed. apna diya hua sadqa wapas na lo.''"
